HEADWORD: Concorporate
<hw>Con*cor"po*rate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>concorporatus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>concorporare</ets>.]</ety>
<def>To unite in one mass or body; to incorporate.</def>
<mark>[Archaic.]</mark> <rj><au>Jer. Taylor.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

